parameters: \n<Wanzworth>Louiesham! Listen, listen! I've heard something amazing!

\n<Wanzworth>The maids were talking about it! I eavesdropped, and
apparently, there's a rumor about an adventurer who's a
beast-person with cat-like traits and incredible strength!

\n<Wanzworth>It has to be big sister, right?! Big sister became an
adventurer! I'm sure of it!
\n<Wanzworth>We have no choice but to go look for her.

\n<Wanzworth>Just gather up the pocket money we've saved and anything
else we need! Let's set out before the night is over!
